Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.47,0:01:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快滾 狗崽子們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.85,0:01:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.81,0:01:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在城裡沒聽人說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.84,0:01:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一帶很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是何人?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.57,0:01:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下一介旅行者 名叫托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心迷了路…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.82,0:01:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛 我是多明妮卡·斯考達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命之恩 感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若雙頭犬去而復返就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要來我家暫避片刻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.93,0:02:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭疼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要從這種傢伙手裡奪遺體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.46,0:02:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝鎧龍的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為領主 守備卻這麼鬆懈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有裝鎧龍在 哪還需其他的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且她本人身手也不容小覷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然已經打過照面 就不能用奇襲作戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住宿 請求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.66,0:02:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安眠 入浴 懇求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒忘記自己的目的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集遺體的事呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記得 當然記得 忘卻 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼看都是忘了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驚愕 變身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是裝鎧龍的魔法嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真方便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 能問下你們之間是什麼關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.61,0:03:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 果然要問這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我們是兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且雖然是血脈相通的兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.46,0:03:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻墜入了禁斷之戀的愛河
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.02,0:03:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 這種背德行為
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家人親屬自然不會允許
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越受反對 燃燒越旺的戀愛之火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 越燒越烈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊地 熊熊地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死也不願分開的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:04:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾一度想到殉情而死 下輩子再長相廝守
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但因最終沒能死成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改變想法 轉為手牽手私奔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而為了甩脫追兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.36,0:04:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們明知這森林危險 卻毅然選擇了穿過它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁斷之戀嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若有機會 我也想嘗試一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁斷之戀?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 在躲過追兵前儘管留在我這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯與阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁斷之戀 我毫不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別聽她瞎說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.35,0:04:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們雖是兄妹 但沒有血緣關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在同一個村落長大而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.10,0:04:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這沒什麼好招待的 但房間可自由使用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有種被人監視的討厭感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來她很是喜歡自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 一直沒看到別人的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她獨自住在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微探察一下?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嘉依卡 你先待在這兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獨自 守候 不可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛骨悚然 恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有使用過的跡象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒有食材
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連老鼠都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 實在不像是領主過的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻燈機嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也太自戀了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貓 存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貓 不戒備
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是沒找到其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連裝鎧龍也不見蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多明妮卡 剛才借用過龍的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.02,0:06:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼龍應該也在這附近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.56,0:06:34.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潛伏在宅子某處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若真的不在 對我們來說也是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 你打算怎麼做?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼做?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明所以 解釋請求
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我準備先用正攻法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面請求她讓出遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若拒絕 則動用武力奪取
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒意見吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從雙頭犬救出 宿處提供
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.40,0:06:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多明妮卡好人 戰鬥否定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:06:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武力行使 不好 恩將仇報
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒說錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你是不是忘了很重要的一點?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多明妮卡可是你的殺父仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對方是怎樣的大善人 處於怎樣的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都和我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的目的 是實現你的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做法由我來想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.95,0:07:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但採用與否 是僱主你的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.87,0:07:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你若這樣優柔寡斷 我們會很難辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tenmu An Gulv NIyaf Oul Alou
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加熱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Boiler
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多明妮卡可是你的殺父仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.53,0:08:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯正確 我錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 遺體 需要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心中 錯綜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多明妮卡 恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 戰鬥 不喜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜘蛛網終於取乾淨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長和我都是亂破師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 對主人所言是絕對服從的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已知 情報
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長滿心只為實現主人嘉依卡的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才逼你做出抉擇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決不是故意在為難你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想請你理解這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要潑熱水了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知是否合您的胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我的戎馬生涯可並不短
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舌頭沒有那麼嬌貴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽聞領主大人您是龍騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何沒見到您的裝鎧龍?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.82,0:10:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它有事離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:14.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對你們來說 也是好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若有龍在身邊走來走去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必也是提心吊膽的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實比較可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 我有一件事想詢問您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.63,0:10:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您應是擊斃賈茲皇帝的八英雄之一吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那您應該持有他的遺體吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能否將其讓給我?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.81,0:10:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼想要那個?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了實現重要之人的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是…你的目的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.68,0:10:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實現她的目的 就是我的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本就覺得你不像尋常百姓了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我確實持有皇帝的遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要就打倒我奪走它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也正好在尋找戰鬥的對手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs43\shad0\pos(640,660)}重要之人…重要之人…重要之人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉 你怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs43\shad0\pos(640,660)}重要之人…重要之人…重要之人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 擅自引發戰鬥是我不對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我也是無可奈何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你一時半會兒下不了決心與她一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可若在這裡浪費時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好那個叫基烈特的騎士會追上我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.95,0:12:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊? 不是因為我沒等你而在生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否 否定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.55,0:12:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 阿卡莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於戰術…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄長你更喜歡胸小 沒腰沒屁股的平板身材嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看不懂兄長你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是不懂你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才說的重要之人 只是修辭而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀紫…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又出來個別的女人?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡給予了我目的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.07,0:12:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給予了我這技藝毫無用武之地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行屍走肉般等死的前亂破師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論她有意無意 我很承她這份恩情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛的告白?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是就不能注意點聽人說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯 昨晚的事 道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.39,0:13:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「武力行使 不好 恩將仇報」的發言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.11,0:13:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我也該說對不起 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我話說得有點太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那擬定下戰略吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.22,0:13:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們久等了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有 準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.47,0:13:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時可開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們或許會收不住手殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能先把遺體位置 告訴我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不著擔心 就憑你們殺不了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到中庭的幻燈機了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是說映出你樣子的那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:13:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堂堂正正來分個勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.16,0:14:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為鋼也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鋼故不怯 鋼故不惑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦逢敵 盡無一切躊躇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為滅此兇器也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鐵血轉化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.93,0:14:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多明妮卡不對勁?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那傢伙才不是多明妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若真是八英雄之一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼對嘉依卡活著毫不驚訝?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿巴爾特伯爵當時可是大吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡的魔法探查 結果如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法探查 宅邸內 有大傢伙 存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宅子內我們都搜遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我說她有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲得好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無需第二劍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起 容不得絲毫大意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但很可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來那傢伙的能力 肉體即使受傷也可立即修復
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝鎧龍的魔法嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要害是額頭 看準這裡下手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過單單刺進去 沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若不像挖削一樣破壞腦部 我都可以復原
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼輕易告訴我沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你就算知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起初我以為你只是個自戀狂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但看你現在的表現 我沒猜錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想假裝人類裝到幾時?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.95,0:16:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的多明妮卡到哪兒去了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰爭結束就離開了你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你大概是被遺棄了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:17:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此還是忘不掉曾並肩作戰的多明妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.44,0:17:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以像這樣 過著被主人包圍的生活?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可悲!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡有錯?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 潛入其中帶來苦痛者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Intruder
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是你的真實面貌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.93,0:17:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.12,0:17:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人們想要的「我的面貌」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算開始生效了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的身體已經動彈不得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿卡莉給你下的毒 正一點一點起效
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.36,0:18:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種東西 休想對我有用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.97,0:18:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利刃呀奔流吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The Ripper
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為人也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要害在額頭對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的多明妮卡去哪兒了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.81,0:19:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.35,0:19:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你殺的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…是病
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰爭的終結改變了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.94,0:19:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了目標的多明妮卡 被病魔輕易帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我獨自留了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打仗時 被那般渴求的裝鎧龍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今已沒人再需要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想忘記曾經需要我的多明妮卡的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多明妮卡直到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.27,0:20:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是抱著渴望戰鬥的心情死去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你也渴望戰鬥?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想實現多明妮卡的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是這變成了你的目的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.29,0:20:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何不了結我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.96,0:20:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這場戰鬥 殺你並非目的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照約定 遺體我們收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.81,0:20:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:20:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,講實話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在想今後該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的話 還是想有個「活著的意義」嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我決定把「殺死你」定為我新的目標!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 剛才的「多明妮卡」現在請叫「芙蕾多妮卡」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.39,0:21:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.85,0:21:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且先幫你把傷給治了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.85,0:21:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了以後能堂堂正正地打敗你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這豈不是說 我們之前的對話全都被你偷聽到了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托魯 貓 無罪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可這貓就是芙蕾多妮卡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且為什麼想殺我的傢伙也一起坐在這兒啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.39,0:21:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同行者 增員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅途快樂 倍僧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.76,0:23:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蕾多妮卡 同伴 加入
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.61,0:23:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝鎧龍最強 底氣倍增
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 芙蕾多妮卡 自由奔放
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.82,0:23:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾消失 一人旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.28,0:23:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周 第五集 「追逐者 受追逐者」
